26
00:01:57.291 --> 00:01:58.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Stop.

27
00:01:58.291 --> 00:02:00.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
