40
00:02:28.750 --> 00:02:30.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ah, well, I was expecting this
a little bit sooner,

41
00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:34.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
but, yup, summoned to the dragon's lair.

42
00:02:34.625 --> 00:02:37.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Go ahead and cancel
the Drill Sergeant's espresso, actually.

43
00:02:37.958 --> 00:02:39.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And, uh, here, why don't you finish mine?

44
00:02:39.583 --> 00:02:41.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-I'm not gonna be needing it anymore...
-[growls]

45
00:02:41.208 --> 00:02:44.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
