49
00:02:52.666 --> 00:02:57.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's been nine months
since I used every ounce of my influence

50
00:02:57.333 --> 00:02:59.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
