of your progress then?

55
00:03:08.583 --> 00:03:10.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Mmm-hmm. Mmm-hmm. Mmm-hmm. Definitely.

56
00:03:10.250 --> 00:03:11.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Sergeant.
-[Drill Sergeant] Yes, sir!

57
00:03:11.916 --> 00:03:13.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sorting and filing:

