64
00:03:27.166 --> 00:03:28.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Well, there you have it.

65
00:03:28.208 --> 00:03:30.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
