and head home then. Too bad.

67
00:03:34.125 --> 00:03:35.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Darn, oh, darn.

68
00:03:35.416 --> 00:03:37.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Stay right where you are.
-No, Dad!

69
00:03:37.458 --> 00:03:39.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
