70
00:03:39.833 --> 00:03:43.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
When will I stop squandering
all these opportunities,

71
00:03:43.125 --> 00:03:45.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
which you so kindly forced me into,

72
00:03:45.333 --> 00:03:46.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
