73
00:03:46.708 --> 00:03:50.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I guess I must really hanker down
and rethink my priorities.

74
00:03:50.583 --> 00:03:53.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
All wrapped up in my silk sheets
with some caviar and a sherry...

75
00:03:53.875 --> 00:03:55.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You still buy the same brand, right?

76
00:03:55.166 --> 00:03:57.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
