Six thousand letters will suffice.

88
00:04:34.875 --> 00:04:36.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Stamped by your own hand.

89
00:04:36.500 --> 00:04:38.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And listen carefully, Jesper.

