or squirm your way out of this one.

97
00:04:57.125 --> 00:05:01.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Dad! Come on!
It's me. Let's talk about this, man.

98
00:05:01.416 --> 00:05:04.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's your son, Jesper! Little Jespie!

