Can I help you put the medals
in the letters

101
00:05:10.291 --> 00:05:12.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and put them in a stamp with the--"

102
00:05:12.166 --> 00:05:13.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
W-w-wait!

103
00:05:13.666 --> 00:05:15.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Do you know how long it took
to press this uniform?

104
00:05:16.500 --> 00:05:18.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I don't either,
but it took somebody hours.

105
00:05:19.041 --> 00:05:20.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hello?

106
00:05:20.541 --> 00:05:23.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Burghard! Finally, a friendly face.
Can you believe what they...

107
