114
00:05:49.333 --> 00:05:52.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This is really wonderful, Father.
Thank you so much.

115
00:05:52.666 --> 00:05:54.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
This is great, Dad.

116
00:05:54.458 --> 00:05:56.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Really, really great.

117
00:06:00.125 --> 00:06:01.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thanks, Dad!

118
00:06:01.333 --> 00:06:02.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[strains and grunts]

119
00:06:02.833 --> 00:06:03.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thank you!

120
00:06:03.791 --> 00:06:06.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I love this terrible coach ride.

121
00:06:06.291 --> 00:06:07.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thank you so much!

122
00:06:07.625 --> 00:06:10.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thank you. Thank you. Thank you. Thank...

123
00:06:24.708 --> 00:06:25.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[huffs]

124
00:06:26.166 --> 00:06:28.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[clears throat]

125
00:06:28.125 --> 00:06:31.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You go back to the intersection.
You make a left at the dead tree.

126
00:06:31.875 --> 00:06:32.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're welcome.

127
00:06:33.416 --> 00:06:35.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
