128
00:06:35.166 --> 00:06:36.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Trust me, you are.

129
00:06:36.708 --> 00:06:39.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[laughs] Funny! Say, nice boat!

130
00:06:39.458 --> 00:06:41.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Any chance you might
actually get on it today?

131
00:06:43.166 --> 00:06:44.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What was that?

132
00:06:44.916 --> 00:06:47.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
New postman. Smeerensburg.

133
00:06:47.416 --> 00:06:49.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
