140
00:07:12.125 --> 00:07:13.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

141
00:07:27.250 --> 00:07:30.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
