306
00:15:58.500 --> 00:16:00.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's so cold and icky!

307
00:16:00.208 --> 00:16:02.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
