[retches]

318
00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:27.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[groans]

319
00:16:30.125 --> 00:16:32.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Fine. Go to the source, I guess.

320
00:16:33.041 --> 00:16:34.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Good morning, madame.

321
00:16:34.250 --> 00:16:36.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm the postman, obviously.

322
00:16:36.083 --> 00:16:37.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
If you have letters you'd like me to send,

323
00:16:37.833 --> 00:16:40.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
you could go scurry ahead
and get them and...

324
00:16:46.250 --> 00:16:47.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hello! Hi! Hi!

325
00:16:47.500 --> 00:16:50.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If you have your letters on you,
