326
00:16:50.125 --> 00:16:50.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts]

327
00:16:52.166 --> 00:16:53.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hmph!

328
00:16:53.083 --> 00:16:55.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Birthday cards? Distant cousin?

329
00:16:55.250 --> 00:16:56.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Deceased notice?

330
00:16:56.291 --> 00:16:57.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Holy mother!

