338
00:17:15.916 --> 00:17:16.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts]

339
00:17:16.833 --> 00:17:19.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
