one thing to say to one another.

341
00:17:24.333 --> 00:17:25.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ah.

342
00:17:25.250 --> 00:17:28.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And they're getting their point across
pretty well without mail.

343
00:17:28.125 --> 00:17:29.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Wouldn't you say?
-Wait, wait, wait.

344
00:17:29.833 --> 00:17:33.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
No letters?
But how am I supposed to get out of...

345
00:17:34.416 --> 00:17:36.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-What the...
-[boy] Hello?

346
00:17:36.250 --> 00:17:38.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
