348
00:17:40.875 --> 00:17:42.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Please?
-Not now, kid.

349
00:17:42.583 --> 00:17:45.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Can't you see I'm busy
trying to figure out how to get...

350
00:17:46.750 --> 00:17:47.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Well, here's a thought.

351
00:17:48.000 --> 00:17:49.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm a postman, see?

352
00:17:49.375 --> 00:17:53.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So I can't give it to you,
but I could mail it to you.

353
00:17:53.541 --> 00:17:55.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[boy] How?
-Couldn't be simpler!

354
00:17:55.291 --> 00:17:58.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I just fold your pretty drawing,
very beautiful by the way,

355
00:17:58.916 --> 00:18:00.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
put it in an envelope like this

356
00:18:00.666 --> 00:18:04.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and then all that's left is postage
so I can put it in the mailbox for you.

357
00:18:05.000 --> 00:18:06.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Postage?
-Yep.

358
00:18:06.416 --> 00:18:09.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You just toss a penny over to me
so I can stamp it,

359
00:18:09.500 --> 00:18:10.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and we're all ready to go.

360
00:18:11.958 --> 00:18:14.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Couldn't you just put it in?

361
00:18:14.541 --> 00:18:16.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aw. Tsk.

362
00:18:16.375 --> 00:18:19.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I really, really would, but I can't.

363
00:18:19.708 --> 00:18:22.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's not a letter
if it doesn't have postage.

364
00:18:22.541 --> 00:18:23.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
See how it works?

365
00:18:24.000 --> 00:18:24.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So what do you say?

366
00:18:25.041 --> 00:18:27.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I get my letter, and you get your drawing.

367
00:18:27.291 --> 00:18:29.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Win-win. You want your drawing, don't you?

368
00:18:29.541 --> 00:18:31.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Um...
-If you don't, I'm gonna keep it.

369
00:18:31.166 --> 00:18:32.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Hmm.
-I love it.

370
00:18:32.541 --> 00:18:33.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I would keep it if I was you,

371
00:18:33.750 --> 00:18:36.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
so I would send this letter
back to myself if I was you.

372
00:18:36.083 --> 00:18:37.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[hounds growling]

373
00:18:37.875 --> 00:18:39.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[boy] Oh, hi, Papa!

374
00:18:39.666 --> 00:18:42.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This nice man says
