381
00:18:54.625 --> 00:18:57.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ah. And that must be the express mail.

382
00:18:58.958 --> 00:19:00.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Jesper] All right, Smeerensburg.

383
00:19:00.333 --> 00:19:01.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
