385
00:19:04.166 --> 00:19:05.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'll have my letters in no time,

386
00:19:05.708 --> 00:19:08.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and then it's bye-bye to you
