396
00:19:47.041 --> 00:19:48.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why, sure I do.

397
00:19:48.375 --> 00:19:51.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
