00:21:15.958 --> 00:21:16.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts]

414
00:21:47.458 --> 00:21:49.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
