433
00:23:18.083 --> 00:23:19.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aah!

434
00:23:19.500 --> 00:23:20.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[pants]

435
00:23:24.583 --> 00:23:25.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[music stops]

436
00:23:25.500 --> 00:23:27.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
