437
00:23:29.875 --> 00:23:31.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aah!

438
00:23:36.333 --> 00:23:37.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[screaming]

439
00:23:50.583 --> 00:23:51.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[screams]

440
00:23:54.291 --> 00:23:55.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
