00:34:07.708 --> 00:34:08.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Look, here.

601
00:34:09.083 --> 00:34:10.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Poor little Herlief.

602
00:34:10.291 --> 00:34:13.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He only has sticks and stones
to play with. So sad.

603
00:34:13.291 --> 00:34:14.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And this one,

604
00:34:14.791 --> 00:34:17.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
little Penny... Patty.

605
00:34:17.083 --> 00:34:19.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Her doll was so old,

606
00:34:19.083 --> 00:34:21.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
it crumbled in her arms
when she came to me.

607
00:34:21.791 --> 00:34:24.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And then Kristoff...
Little, ugly Kristoff.

608
00:34:25.333 --> 00:34:26.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
This little...

609
00:34:33.208 --> 00:34:34.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tonight, same time.

610
00:34:35.916 --> 00:34:39.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Great! What, "same time"?
You mean, dead of night?

611
00:34:39.875 --> 00:34:42.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-I can just take the toys now.
-No. I go with you.

612
00:34:42.250 --> 00:34:44.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
There's no need
for you to come with me, really.

613
00:34:44.541 --> 00:34:45.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It might be against the law

614
00:34:45.958 --> 00:34:48.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
for a noncertified postman
to ride with me.

615
00:34:48.958 --> 00:34:50.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I have to check the rule book.

616
00:34:50.875 --> 00:34:54.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Great. Tonight, then. I'll see you then.
Good talk. Good talk.

617
00:34:57.250 --> 00:34:59.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[laughing and exclaiming]

618
00:35:09.541 --> 00:35:10.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

619
00:35:10.458 --> 00:35:11.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

620
00:35:17.291 --> 00:35:19.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[children laughing]
-[hounds whining]

621
00:35:25.333 --> 00:35:27.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Whoa! Whoo!

622
00:35:27.375 --> 00:35:28.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

623
00:35:28.791 --> 00:35:29.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

624
00:35:29.708 --> 00:35:30.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[giggles]

625
00:35:30.875 --> 00:35:31.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

626
00:35:31.958 --> 00:35:33.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[woman gasps]

627
00:35:33.625 --> 00:35:35.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Oh, oh!
-[gasps]

628
00:35:35.583 --> 00:35:36.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

629
00:35:39.750 --> 00:35:40.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[man] Playing!

630
00:35:40.750 --> 00:35:42.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Playing, I tell you.

631
00:35:42.666 --> 00:35:44.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
With an Ellingboe!

632
00:35:44.083 --> 00:35:46.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[councilman 1] An Ellingboe, no less!
-[councilman 2] In all my years!

633
00:35:46.500 --> 00:35:48.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Did you all hear that?
-Unacceptable.

634
00:35:48.583 --> 00:35:50.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[man] I don't know how it happened.
-[yelps]

635
00:35:50.083 --> 00:35:52.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I turned away for one second...

636
00:35:54.500 --> 00:35:56.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And then I saw it.

637
00:35:56.083 --> 00:35:58.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I brought her as soon as I could, sir.

638
00:35:58.208 --> 00:36:00.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-That's just wrong! Wrong, I say!
-Inconceivable!

639
00:36:00.541 --> 00:36:02.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-What are we going to do?
-Unthinkable!

640
00:36:02.708 --> 00:36:05.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hmm. This is bad. Very bad.

641
00:36:05.416 --> 00:36:08.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Worst I've ever seen, really.
What were you thinking, kid?

642
00:36:08.625 --> 00:36:09.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Don't you know that--

643
00:36:09.666 --> 00:36:12.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Krums and Ellingboes don't mix.

644
00:36:13.541 --> 00:36:15.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-But why?
-"Why?" he asks!

645
00:36:15.458 --> 00:36:16.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-See what I mean?
-[councilwoman] Why?

646
00:36:17.000 --> 00:36:18.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I don't know what to do!

647
00:36:18.750 --> 00:36:21.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Please help us, miss! I beg you!

648
00:36:23.083 --> 00:36:23.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

649
00:36:24.000 --> 00:36:25.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[squeals]

650
00:36:29.500 --> 00:36:32.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Do you know what this is, little boy?

651
00:36:33.125 --> 00:36:36.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
This is tradition!

652
00:36:36.916 --> 00:36:42.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Centuries of glorious hatred,
passed down through generations!

653
00:36:43.000 --> 00:36:45.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
There was the hundred-day brawl of '45.

654
00:36:45.916 --> 00:36:47.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Which we totally won!

655
00:36:47.583 --> 00:36:49.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The maritime game of chicken.

656
00:36:49.583 --> 00:36:52.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The Great Mooning of '86.

657
00:36:52.833 --> 00:36:53.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

658
00:36:54.458 --> 00:36:56.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So, if there's something we know...

659
00:36:56.666 --> 00:36:59.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
...going back as far as we can remember...

660
00:36:59.333 --> 00:37:01.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
...it's that a Krum
despises an Ellingboe...

661
00:37:01.916 --> 00:37:05.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
...and an Ellingboe can't stand a Krum!

662
00:37:09.958 --> 00:37:11.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That is why.

663
00:37:11.958 --> 00:37:12.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

664
00:37:12.958 --> 00:37:19.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Now, I just know you didn't mean to
disrespect all of that heritage, right?

665
00:37:20.041 --> 00:37:23.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Right.
-And it won't happen again,

666
00:37:23.208 --> 00:37:24.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
will it?

667
00:37:25.541 --> 00:37:27.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Of course not.

668
00:37:27.666 --> 00:37:30.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Now, tell me all about
where this pretty thing came from.

669
00:37:35.625 --> 00:37:36.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ugh.

670
00:37:37.458 --> 00:37:40.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Let me guess.
Leaving it at the gate not an option?

671
00:37:43.083 --> 00:37:45.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You really have a way with words,
you know?

672
00:37:46.291 --> 00:37:49.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Of course, you don't...
Of course, don't even answer that...

673
00:37:51.125 --> 00:37:51.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[groans]

674
00:37:52.958 --> 00:37:54.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

675
00:37:55.708 --> 00:37:56.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts]

676
00:37:57.083 --> 00:37:58.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Whoa, whoa, whoa. No, no, no!

677
00:37:58.958 --> 00:37:59.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[screams]

678
00:38:00.041 --> 00:38:01.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts]

679
00:38:01.083 --> 00:38:02.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Stop, stop, stop!

680
00:38:02.958 --> 00:38:04.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Stop! Stop!

681
00:38:05.750 --> 00:38:06.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aah!

682
00:38:07.666 --> 00:38:08.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[screaming]

683
00:38:13.458 --> 00:38:14.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[groaning]

684
00:38:32.083 --> 00:38:33.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[sighs]

685
00:38:34.375 --> 00:38:36.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[snoring]

686
00:38:38.791 --> 00:38:39.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Whoa! Whoa!

687
00:38:40.041 --> 00:38:41.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[screams]

688
00:38:41.416 --> 00:38:43.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-You rotten vermin!
-[children giggling]

689
00:38:44.916 --> 00:38:46.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[yawning]

690
00:38:47.333 --> 00:38:49.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[child 1] Me, me, me!
-[child 2] Pick me!

691
00:38:49.083 --> 00:38:50.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[child 1] Out of the way!
-[child 3] Mine first!

692
00:38:50.375 --> 00:38:51.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I want a bicycle!

693
00:38:51.500 --> 00:38:53.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Tell Mr. Klaus I want a bicycle!
-Shut up!

694
00:38:53.166 --> 00:38:54.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Take my letter! Take my letter!
-Mine! Me!

695
00:38:54.958 --> 00:38:56.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Me first! Me first! A doll!

696
00:38:56.958 --> 00:39:00.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
-Me! Me! Me!
-Okay! Okay! Single line! Chop-chop!

697
00:39:00.541 --> 00:39:02.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Fall back! All right. Everyone, in line.

698
00:39:02.875 --> 00:39:04.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-There you go.
-Get out! Move.

699
00:39:04.083 --> 00:39:07.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Letter? Good. Letter? Good.

700
00:39:07.083 --> 00:39:09.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Got it. Get out of here.
Great. Move along.

701
00:39:11.750 --> 00:39:14.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[speaking Saami]

702
00:39:14.208 --> 00:39:18.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-What's wrong with her mouth?
-She's not from here. She's Saami.

703
00:39:19.041 --> 00:39:22.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[speaking Saami]

704
00:39:22.166 --> 00:39:26.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Right, that's nice. But I see no letter,
so please come back when you have one.

705
00:39:26.375 --> 00:39:27.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Have a nice day.

706
00:39:27.458 --> 00:39:29.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bye-bye. Okay, any other letters?

707
00:39:29.500 --> 00:39:30.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[boy] Here! Here! Here!
-[girl] Me, me, me!

708
00:39:30.666 --> 00:39:32.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Good. The rest, you know the deal.

709
00:39:32.500 --> 00:39:33.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No letter, no toy.

710
00:39:33.875 --> 00:39:35.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But we don't know how to write.

711
00:39:35.916 --> 00:39:37.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[yawns]

712
00:39:37.625 --> 00:39:39.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tough luck, kid.

713
00:39:39.291 --> 00:39:41.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Wait, you know what you could do?

714
00:39:53.083 --> 00:39:55.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[whistling]

715
00:39:55.625 --> 00:39:57.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-What are you doing?
-Aah!

716
00:39:57.250 --> 00:39:59.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Telling children to go to school
to learn to write?

717
00:39:59.708 --> 00:40:00.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What is wrong with you?

718
00:40:00.666 --> 00:40:02.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah, yes. What I meant to do--

719
00:40:02.375 --> 00:40:03.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Listen to me, Postman.
-[whimpers]

720
00:40:03.625 --> 00:40:06.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Whatever you're doing, leave me out of it.

721
00:40:06.166 --> 00:40:08.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I have been rotting away here
for five years,

722
00:40:08.916 --> 00:40:10.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and I am so close to getting out.

723
00:40:10.416 --> 00:40:12.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I am not about to let you mess it all up.

724
00:40:12.666 --> 00:40:13.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You got it?

725
00:40:13.625 --> 00:40:17.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
These children wasting away
without a proper education?

726
00:40:17.125 --> 00:40:18.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I mean...

727
00:40:18.208 --> 00:40:19.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[chuckles]

728
00:40:19.541 --> 00:40:22.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Forgive me, I'm kind of a dreamer, but...
isn't that why we do it?

729
00:40:22.958 --> 00:40:24.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hmm? Hmm?

730
00:40:24.125 --> 00:40:25.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why you became a teacher?

731
00:40:26.041 --> 00:40:27.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So you could make a difference?

732
00:40:27.750 --> 00:40:28.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[groans]

733
00:40:29.000 --> 00:40:31.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts and huffs]

734
00:40:31.083 --> 00:40:32.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[panting]

735
00:40:32.208 --> 00:40:34.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ah. Young love.

736
00:40:34.541 --> 00:40:35.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Takes me back, you know?

737
00:40:35.750 --> 00:40:39.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The intense looks,
the palpitation of the heart.

738
00:40:39.333 --> 00:40:41.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The whimpering
and the soiling of the pants, no.

739
00:40:41.833 --> 00:40:43.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I can't relate to so much.

740
00:40:43.375 --> 00:40:44.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[sighs]

741
00:40:48.500 --> 00:40:50.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So you go to sleep,
and when you wake up in the morning,

742
00:40:50.916 --> 00:40:52.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
the present is right there
by the fireplace!

743
00:40:52.791 --> 00:40:54.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah, Mr. Klaus is amazing!

744
00:40:55.041 --> 00:40:57.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[boy chuckles] Yeah, he's awesome.
-Yeah!

745
00:40:57.166 --> 00:40:59.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Klaus"? "Awesome"?

746
00:40:59.250 --> 00:41:02.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He's huge,
but he can squeeze down any chimney!

747
00:41:02.208 --> 00:41:03.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Really? How?
-I don't know.

748
00:41:03.958 --> 00:41:04.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Magic, I guess.

749
00:41:05.041 --> 00:41:06.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ow! [grunts]

750
00:41:08.666 --> 00:41:09.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
