01:07:25.291 --> 01:07:28.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
After... After she was gone,

1197
01:07:29.875 --> 01:07:32.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I... I guess I got lost.

1198
01:07:33.458 --> 01:07:38.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She loved birds,
so I just kept making birdhouses.

1199
01:07:40.708 --> 01:07:41.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But then...

1200
01:07:42.208 --> 01:07:43.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Then you showed up.

1201
01:07:44.583 --> 01:07:49.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Delivering these toys,
seeing the joy they bring to children,

1202
01:07:49.791 --> 01:07:51.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I thought I'd never feel this again.

1203
01:07:52.291 --> 01:07:55.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And I have you to thank for it, my friend.

1204
01:07:55.916 --> 01:07:57.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So... thank you.

1205
01:07:59.500 --> 01:08:00.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Of course.

1206
01:08:02.000 --> 01:08:04.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Hey, you know what? We're doing it!
-What?

1207
01:08:04.791 --> 01:08:06.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Doing what?
-The Christmas thing!

1208
01:08:06.541 --> 01:08:08.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We're making all those toys!

1209
01:08:08.333 --> 01:08:10.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-That's what she would've wanted.
-Really?

1210
01:08:10.125 --> 01:08:12.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Yeah, really!
And with a whole year of planning,

1211
01:08:12.875 --> 01:08:15.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-we can expand to more villages next year.
-Next year?

1212
01:08:15.500 --> 01:08:17.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-And more the year after that!
-But I won't...

1213
01:08:17.375 --> 01:08:19.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I mean, who knows
what's gonna happen next year?

1214
01:08:19.166 --> 01:08:20.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I might not even--

1215
01:08:20.291 --> 01:08:23.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[chuckles] What're you going on about?
Let's go! No time to lose!

1216
01:08:23.833 --> 01:08:25.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[sighs]

1217
01:08:25.166 --> 01:08:26.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[softly] I might not even be here.

1218
01:08:36.375 --> 01:08:39.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[children] <i> One, two, three, four, five </i>

1219
01:08:39.916 --> 01:08:43.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i> Once I caught a fish alive </i>

1220
01:08:43.666 --> 01:08:46.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i> Six, seven, eight, nine, ten </i>

1221
01:08:47.458 --> 01:08:50.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i> Then I let it go again </i>

1222
01:08:51.000 --> 01:08:54.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i> Why did you let it go? </i>

1223
01:08:54.250 --> 01:08:57.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i> Because it bit my finger so! </i>

1224
01:08:57.250 --> 01:09:00.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i> Which finger did it bite? </i>

1225
01:09:00.333 --> 01:09:03.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i> This little finger on my right! </i>

1226
01:09:03.375 --> 01:09:04.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[Alva] Good job!
-[children] Yay!

1227
01:09:05.041 --> 01:09:06.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
All right, that's it for today.

1228
01:09:06.875 --> 01:09:08.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And, um... homework!

1229
01:09:08.375 --> 01:09:10.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh! Uh... I forgot about homework.

1230
01:09:10.583 --> 01:09:12.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-You know what? No homework.
-[boy laughs]

1231
01:09:12.125 --> 01:09:13.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Am I the best teacher ever or what?

1232
01:09:13.833 --> 01:09:14.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What...

1233
01:09:15.375 --> 01:09:16.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-happened here?
-Oh.

1234
01:09:17.250 --> 01:09:20.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Yeah, I thought
I would give the place an update.

1235
01:09:20.166 --> 01:09:22.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Everybody knows rotting fish is so over.

1236
01:09:22.750 --> 01:09:24.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
How did you pay for this?

1237
01:09:24.458 --> 01:09:25.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hmm?

1238
01:09:25.750 --> 01:09:29.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Your savings?
-Well, not all of it.

1239
01:09:29.166 --> 01:09:31.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Actually, yeah, all of it.
But check it out.

1240
01:09:31.333 --> 01:09:32.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I think it looks pretty good.

1241
01:09:32.541 --> 01:09:35.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What about starting
far, far away from here?

1242
01:09:35.750 --> 01:09:36.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Where's that Alva?

1243
01:09:36.791 --> 01:09:38.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Someone would have to be pretty stupid

1244
01:09:38.833 --> 01:09:40.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
to want to leave this place now.
[chuckles]

1245
01:09:40.500 --> 01:09:41.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Don't you think?

1246
01:09:42.500 --> 01:09:44.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I... guess.

1247
01:09:45.416 --> 01:09:47.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You guess? Oh, wow.

1248
01:09:47.375 --> 01:09:49.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You have no idea what you've done, do you?

1249
01:09:50.250 --> 01:09:52.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ugh. Come on. I'll show you.

1250
01:09:58.333 --> 01:10:00.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Now, would you take a look at that?

1251
01:10:00.291 --> 01:10:02.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[laughter and indistinct chatter]

1252
01:10:07.208 --> 01:10:10.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i> Silent night </i>

1253
01:10:11.041 --> 01:10:14.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i> Holy night </i>

1254
01:10:18.000 --> 01:10:19.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Merry Christmas, Miss. Alva!

1255
01:10:19.291 --> 01:10:20.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Merry Christmas, Mr. Postman!
-Merry Christmas.

1256
01:10:20.625 --> 01:10:21.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Good evening, Postman Johanssen.

1257
01:10:22.041 --> 01:10:23.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Hello.
